		    <title outputclass="H4H30x" xtrf="Grey" class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">570.203-3</ph> Soliciting offers.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d969e13">
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d960e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The contracting officer must solicit offers by providing each prospective offeror a proposed short form lease GSA Form 3626 or SFO. The short form lease or SFO must:</p>
					          <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d969e23">
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Describe the Government’s requirements.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e36">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 List all award factors, including price or cost, and any significant subfactors that the contracting officer will consider in awarding the lease.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e45">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 State the relative importance of the evaluation factors and subfactors.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e54">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 State whether all evaluation factors other than cost or price, when combined, are either:</p>
							              <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d969e60">
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d960e64">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Significantly more important than cost or price.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d960e73">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Approximately equal in importance to cost or price.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            audience="GSAR"
                            outputclass="Grey_H7_i_ii_iii"
                            xtrf="Grey"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                              xtrf="Grey"
                              class="- topic/p "
                              id="d960e82">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Significantly less important than cost or price.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e93">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Include either in full text or by reference, applicable FAR provisions and contract clauses required by <xref href="GSAM-i1864464.dita#i1864464"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">570.6</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d960e106">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Include sustainable design requirements.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li id="i1854955"
                otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d960e117">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             As necessary, review with prospective offerors the Government’s requirements, pricing matters, evaluation procedures and submission of offers.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
